Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C2305210> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Closed' compared to 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in the top 10 longest process variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to the next activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases where 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' also occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Standard deviation of 'Accepted + Wait' duration across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases ending with 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to the first occurrence of 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases with more than one occurrence of this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait occurs

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in the variant with the highest performance score
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C2305210> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in the variant with the lowest performance score
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases with 'Low' impact versus 'High' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of impact filtered by the function ma == 'Low' where ma is the last value of impact
